---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Shavkatov Fayzulloh haqida — SEO, AEO va GEO mutaxassis"
  description="Shavkatov Fayzulloh — SEO, AEO va GEO bo'yicha mutaxassis, Darslinker.uz asoschisi. Bizneslarni Google va AI qidiruvda topga chiqaradi."
>
  <article class="about" id="aboutContent" transition:animate="fade">
    <section class="about-intro">
      <div class="about-uz">
        <h1 class="sr-only">Shavkatov Fayzulloh haqida</h1>
        <p class="lead-uz">
          <strong>SEO, AEO va GEO bo'yicha mutaxassis.</strong> Bizneslarni Google va AI qidiruv tizimlarida topga chiqaraman.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-en" style="display: none;">
        <h1 class="sr-only">About Shavkatov Fayzulloh</h1>
        <p class="lead-en">
          <strong>SEO, AEO and GEO specialist.</strong> I bring businesses to the top in Google and AI search.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="personal">
    <div class="about-uz">
      <h3>Qisqa qilaman:</h3>

      <p>Sahifa rezyume uchun emas, bu yerda "hammasi reja bo'yicha" degan gap ham yo'q.</p>

      <p>Bu fikrlar to'planadigan joy. Ba'zan ishlar yaxshiligida, ba'zan esa ichimda savollar ko'payib ketganda yozaman.</p>

      <p>Asosan SEO/AEO jarayoni yoziladi. Qanday kechayotgani va menga qanday ta'sir qilayotgani bilan birga.</p>

      <p>Blogdagi ba'zi fikrlarim "tasodifan" juda aqlli chiqib qolishi mumkin, qolganlari esa kayfiyatga bog'liq. Baland ovozli motivatsiya yo'q, qat'iy formulalar ham.</p>

      <p>Agar o'qib turib "bu yerda o'zimga bog'liq nimadir bor" degan fikr kelsa - demak siz to'g'ri joydasiz.</p>

      <p class="signature">Shavkatov Fayzulloh</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-en" style="display: none;">
      <h1 class="sr-only">About Shavkatov Fayzulloh</h1>
      <h3>Short:</h3>

      <p>This page is not a resume. And there's no "everything is going according to plan" here.</p>

      <p>It's a place where thoughts are collected. Sometimes I write when things are going well, sometimes when questions start piling up in my head.</p>

      <p>Mostly, I write about the SEO/AEO process — how it unfolds and how it affects me along the way.</p>

      <p>Some thoughts in the blog may "accidentally" sound very smart, others depend entirely on my mood. There's no loud motivation here, no rigid formulas either.</p>

      <p>If, while reading, you think, "There's something here that relates to me," then you're in the right place.</p>

      <p class="signature">Shavkatov Fayzulloh</p>
    </div>
    </section>

    <CTA />

    <footer>
      <a href="/" id="backLink">&larr; Ortga</a>
      <a href="/blog" id="blogLink">Blog &rarr;</a>
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  const backLink = document.getElementById('backLink');

  const setLang = (lang: string) => {
    document.querySelectorAll('.about-uz').forEach((el) => {
      (el as HTMLElement).style.display = lang === 'en' ? 'none' : 'block';
    });
    document.querySelectorAll('.about-en').forEach((el) => {
      (el as HTMLElement).style.display = lang === 'en' ? 'block' : 'none';
    });
    if (backLink) backLink.innerHTML = lang === 'en' ? '&larr; Back' : '&larr; Ortga';
  };

  setLang(localStorage.getItem('lang') || 'uz');
  document.addEventListener('langchange', (e: any) => setLang(e.detail));
</script>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    max-width: 560px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-intro {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(118, 118, 118, 0.3);
  }

  .lead-uz, .lead-en {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .lead-uz strong, .lead-en strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

.sr-only {
    position: absolute;
    width: 1px;
    height: 1px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: -1px;
    overflow: hidden;
    clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
    border: 0;
  }

  .about h3 {
    color: #b3b3b3;
  }

  .about p {
    color: #b3b3b3;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .signature {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    color: #b3b3b3;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  footer {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(118, 118, 118, 0.5);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  footer a {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  footer a:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
</style>
